299
00:21:13,672 --> 00:21:16,915
<i>12 reasons why
the Clotaire-Chaillot Residence</i>

300
00:21:17,309 --> 00:21:19,721
<i>is the most elegant in Paris.</i>

301
00:21:19,845 --> 00:21:24,021
<i>First, the façade
is white Carrara marble.</i>

302
00:21:24,383 --> 00:21:28,627
<i>Secondly, Turbo and Maserati
designed the lobby fountains</i>

303
00:21:28,788 --> 00:21:31,632
<i>that occupy the ground floor.</i>

304
00:21:31,791 --> 00:21:34,294
<i>Alessandro Forlani painted the murals.</i>

305
00:21:34,460 --> 00:21:38,340
