to the charm of these halls</i>

306
00:21:38,497 --> 00:21:41,000
<i>and can also be heard in the elevators.</i>

307
00:21:41,367 --> 00:21:44,280
<i>Thirdly, the elevators are automatic,</i>

308
00:21:44,436 --> 00:21:47,280
<i>very fast, lined with stainless steel.</i>

309
00:21:47,439 --> 00:21:50,352
Where did you learn to grow flowers

310
00:21:50,543 --> 00:21:51,886
and to garden?

311
00:21:52,044 --> 00:21:54,820
I don't really know.

312
00:21:54,980 --> 00:21:57,586
I follow my instinct.

313
00:21:57,750 --> 00:22:01,994
You must have learned.
It's hard to grow pansies in pots.

314
00:22:02,955 --> 00:22:06,630
I sow them in my garden,
then replant them.

315
00:22:06,792 --> 00:22:08,794
You spend much time on it'?

316
00:22:08,961 --> 00:22:10,941
Not so much.

317
00:22:11,096 --> 00:22:12,769
When you're not working?

318
00:22:12,932 --> 00:22:15,378
Well, I'm out of work now.

319
00:22:15,534 --> 00:22:19,311
Otherwise, I do it on weekends.

320
00:22:19,471 --> 00:22:21,542
I water them in the evening.

321
00:22:21,707 --> 00:22:23,448
What do you think about?

322
00:22:24,343 --> 00:22:27,324
I think they're pretty,
I love flowers.

323
00:22:27,479 --> 00:22:28,981
You're from the country?

324
00:22:29,348 --> 00:22:33,592
I was born in the country.
But I've been here a long time.

325
00:22:33,886 --> 00:22:36,389
How do you feel about plastic flowers?

326
00:22:37,056 --> 00:22:40,799
They're nice too,
but not worth real ones.

327
00:22:40,960 --> 00:22:43,804
- You have plastic flowers?
- In my garden.

328
00:22:43,963 --> 00:22:48,708
You mix them with real flowers
so they'll look natural?

329
00:22:48,868 --> 00:22:52,008
They're there as the others
haven't bloomed.

330
00:22:53,038 --> 00:22:55,951
What gave you the idea
of growing flowers?

331
00:22:56,876 --> 00:22:58,583
It was just an idea.

332
00:22:59,478 --> 00:23:03,688
