<i>And the moon is full, no vacancies</i>

889
01:00:40,770 --> 01:00:45,276
<i>Lovely May, you've left your daydreams</i>

890
01:00:45,642 --> 01:00:50,057
<i>To grow roots in the streets of Paris</i>

891
01:00:50,213 --> 01:00:54,286
<i>Your scarf cast over lying eyes</i>

892
